9
00:00:47,833 --> 00:00:51,034
AI represents the concepts of machines

10
00:00:51,475 --> 00:00:55,036
that can learn, reason, and act for themselves.

11
00:00:56,876 --> 00:00:58,877
Machine learning is a subset of AI.

12
00:00:58,897 --> 00:01:01,118
There are programs using statistics

13
00:01:01,878 --> 00:01:04,199
to find patterns in massive amount of data.

14
00:01:04,847 --> 00:01:08,290
and use those patterns to make predictions on new data.

15
00:01:10,892 --> 00:01:14,574
Deep learning can be seen as machine learning on steroids.

16
00:01:16,075 --> 00:01:20,899
It extracts layered features, or learned from complex data,

17
00:01:21,720 --> 00:01:23,141
in order to make a prediction.

18
00:01:24,061 --> 00:01:27,484
And because it analyzes the data through many hidden layers,

19
00:01:27,944 --> 00:01:29,565
it is called deep learning.

20
00:01:29,585 --> 00:01:33,088
Don't worry, I will explain more in detail what it means later.

21
00:01:35,882 --> 00:01:38,684
