22
00:01:38,884 --> 00:01:41,786
In reality, the most recent developments

23
00:01:42,306 --> 00:01:43,808
deal with deep learning.

24
00:01:45,749 --> 00:01:49,652
The hype of deep learning is at its maximum.

25
00:01:50,072 --> 00:01:51,613
And because it's still exploratory,

26
00:01:52,194 --> 00:01:55,997
we live a time of excessive expectations followed

27
00:01:56,497 --> 00:01:58,098
by excessive disappointments.

28
00:02:00,240 --> 00:02:02,141
So what I hope to accomplish today

29
00:02:03,042 --> 00:02:05,544
is to provide with a more concrete view.

30
00:02:06,245 --> 00:02:10,827
of what machine learning really is, can, and can't do.

31
